000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63178ae4fbb06ee7cefcc37e731f3a868b223cd4","tid":1462424,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:44:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"718a00f1b485d8d9de6e83ca4a6b0ee3f74efc8f","tid":1462424,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:45:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb4541b9f1d964eb26066c9b845477d495488a3e","tid":1462424,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"大家要快d開始傾<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大方向</span></strong></span><br />\n3毛5毛開始想<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">重施故技</span></span></strong>用斟酌「阻人上機」個point黎<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化大家</span></span></strong><br />\n但記得大家塞爆機場個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">目的</span></strong></span>就係要<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">癱瘓機場從而阻人上機</span></span></strong>以造成<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">巨大經濟損失</span></span></strong><br />\n建議集中火力搵出影響力最大嘅時間<br />\n睇下邊段時間最多人能響應，找出平衡<br />\n用隔日形式塞爆<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以最大化個運動成效</span></span></strong><br />\n隔日嘅好處係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">避免大家過勞和積累</span></strong>過多<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">外國民怨</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>個人認為呢位師兄言之有物<br />\n希望大家可以集思廣益</strong></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好 | LIHKG<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1459515/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地團結一致</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPush"},{"pid":"7fac3131ac3b94fe610c4e459a41b90abb624090","tid":1462424,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:45:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3957095542faf9bdb196fbc1257234dcf135fceb","tid":1462424,"uid":164517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:45:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b05e2843afb48aae7c4c2a8ed4edf30b61c59f1","tid":1462424,"uid":78552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:45:47.000Z","msg":"諗下外國人返到自己國家會講咩<br />\n我比一班黑衣人阻上機<br />\n完全唔會理解到係黑警令到班黑衣人咁做<br />\n之前接機做既宣傳就白費！<br />\n<br />\n琴日唔阻人機管局取消航班<br />\n屌既都係屌機管局<br />\n今日阻人上機<br />\n屌既係我地<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好阻人上機呀</span></span>"},{"pid":"9f862fb9e12582a00fa9ed84b50c1b1ea0f4a339","tid":1462424,"uid":158108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b0b2b8524c5165b916a2d1a0f012f79ec83eec8b","tid":1462424,"uid":305482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:36:49.000Z","msg":"不分化<br />\n<br />\n但真係唔好阻旅客"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:46:04.000Z","msg":"認同且分享"},{"pid":"ce6d0caa105bc7f0b2b1d1180fa9c9775b748179","tid":1462424,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:46:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370bd4bec6afcba3e8d235c4d35453c3c519f9f5","tid":1462424,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:46:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fcb4dee8bb6841b38737ba3e5b05ba3d9d58edb4","tid":1462424,"uid":236073,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:46:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2043cf8e52d750ab5c8274825acb5e51e1e230c3","tid":1462424,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:46:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9d7cd05ec289a5422ba194c1ad55135c71e53643","tid":1462424,"uid":267959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:46:59.000Z","msg":"你們不能跟政府一樣強迫人"},{"pid":"ca1e78f7b7a3e13d7414776ec8f1bf700ca86c64","tid":1462424,"uid":293256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd6b24d54716eb9428ddcc72a5ea02a460558c90","tid":1462424,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:32:53.000Z","msg":"我話你知 黑衫入面一定有鬼<br />\n啲鬼就一定係想阻到旅客上唔到機<br />\n矛頭就會指向示威者<br />\n政府就搵藉口行動<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>建議:發現有人阻旅客阻交通<br />\n拉走佢 佢唔走就係鬼</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地輸出既係比人知道 政府黑暗<br />\n塞爆機場 令到機管局取消航班<br />\n而唔係人手令旅客上唔到機<br />\n因為上唔到機係人為，無得賠<br />\n<br />\n雖然不分化不割蓆<br />\n但唔該行動前用下腦 <br />\n唔好比人覺得你係鬼好無？<br />\n<br />\n#721 811"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:47:19.000Z","msg":"推！又話兄弟爬山各分工，講到明和你飛，塞嚟做乜先"},{"pid":"bb2d1bda51844942bcaf8f18b5dce45db3ad8304","tid":1462424,"uid":82241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:48:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a8ab549dd12d736632511c7befb44860a2c5d55","tid":1462424,"uid":3280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母分化撚<br />\n去得機場班友就係想擺停個機場<br />\n點塞你覺得對遊客有咩分別"},{"pid":"36ee563f55a640c54a44a96aebe2c5500467cd40","tid":1462424,"uid":14080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"你收皮啦 琴日塞又唔叫阻嘅"},{"pid":"8507f929aa96636ceb320365402ec7435b4024b5","tid":1462424,"uid":42942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8831e54a8fb34f80e0ea314c9873c10850627aa","tid":1462424,"uid":37440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"不分化不割蓆 目標都係林鄭"},{"pid":"039d4c3156e30216872e092efe793f0df0413078","tid":1462424,"uid":282118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T10:49:09.000Z","msg":"文宣同阻人係有分別<br />\n十卜樓主"},{"pid":"6df2d3d8fefd3ff4882a71682d9a90de71a502c0","tid":1462424,"uid":212646,"l